<tableCitation id="9F2DAB03D367CD673DE4C647F8EC598F" captionStart="Table 2" captionStartId="T2" captionText="Table 2. Comparing the diagnostics of Sedum lipingense sp. nov., S. subtile and S. bulbiferum." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/642C24D9DF28ACBFE5253E5E4C6375B0" pageId="4" pageNumber="129" tableUuid="642C24D9DF28ACBFE5253E5E4C6375B0">2</tableCitation>
).
</paragraph>
